  "body": "I am wondering how can I use it to sign transactions with ethereumjs-tx?\r\nThe sign() method of ethereumjs-tx accepts private key Buffer as mentioned in docs:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereumjs/ethereumjs-tx/blob/master/docs/index.md#sign\r\n\r\n**How can I use truffle-hdwallet-provider to sign the transaction?**\r\n\r\n_This is the duplicate_ of https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-hdwallet-provider/issues/73 and moved here because that repo is going to be archived.",
